nl.ctmm.trait.proteomics.qcviewer.input

Class ReportUnit

  • java.lang.Object
    • nl.ctmm.trait.proteomics.qcviewer.input.ReportUnit

  • public class ReportUnit
extends java.lang.Object
    The object of this class represents report of single msreading.

    The ReportUnit class contains information from an MS run generated by the QC tool that are displayed by the QC report viewer.

    Author:
    Pravin Pawar, Freek de Bruijn
